{"tid":2357981,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"Uber跪低｜Uber遭多國封殺出售業務　現職司機悲觀：做到佢冇咗為止","createTime":"2021-01-07T22:12:41.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-20T13:13:12.000Z","uid":130626,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"6bcc2048f4250167d41422f21b9615e2a8b4f4d8","tid":2357981,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T22:12:42.000Z","msg":"Uber除了在港經營受到非議，過去在中港澳、東南亞等多地，亦被指違反當地交通條例而遭多國封殺，至2018年初更撤出東南亞8個國家，將業務售予另一租車公司Grab。去年Uber更因疫情衝擊，全球裁減人手逾6千人，佔整體員工四分之一，同時關閉全球45間辦公室及180間司機服務中心。現時Uber業務在港雖仍活躍，但屢遭警方放蛇拘捕司機，不少現職司機坦言已作心理準備，「Uber一日喺香港嘅，我哋咪一日繼續做囉，直至到佢冇咗為止。」<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20210108/3HGZ7Z5LLBFNLASY54XX2NGZAI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20210108%2F3HGZ7Z5LLBFNLASY54XX2NGZAI%2F&d=vTNdr7lgiRBdtcQZ4wg6z%2FDXWQKahOldmH8%2Bpia8yKE%3D&h=1e23efbc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20210108%2F3HGZ7Z5LLBFNLASY54XX2NGZAI%2F&h=811202c7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20210108/3HGZ7Z5LLBFNLASY54XX2NGZAI/</a>"},{"pid":"ff81de94e1f434767eb03379f7150659a2282ef4","tid":2357981,"uid":86199,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T22:34:04.000Z","msg":"將業務售予另一租車公司Grab。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nGrab唔俾人封殺？"},{"pid":"1662f05efc66718d9988de21798d210df41a58ac","tid":2357981,"uid":66365,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T22:47:03.000Z","msg":"抵死啦咁撚垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd809f62970a2b689c90347571a72f54d49d084c","tid":2357981,"uid":212623,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T22:47:49.000Z","msg":"抵<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/throw.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 